## Architecture

This project uses **FastAPI + SQLAlchemy 2.0 (async)**:

- **src/main.py** — FastAPI application with CORS middleware
- **src/core/config.py** — Pydantic settings with env file support
- **src/core/database.py** — SQLAlchemy async engine (singleton)
- **src/routers/api.py** — Route modules (hello, users CRUD)

Key conventions:

- Async endpoints with Pydantic v2 validation
- Email validation at route boundary
- Standard `{ success, data, error }` JSON response shape
